trans-unit.source: APPENDIX: Response Codes for X12 Bridges
trans-unit.target: APPENDIX: Response Codes for X12 Bridges

trans-unit.source: Lists the possible response codes you might encounter when a message is processed using the X12 Receive or X12 Send pipelines in the <token>tpm_portal</token>.
trans-unit.target: Lists the possible response codes you might encounter when a message is processed using the X12 Receive or X12 Send pipelines in the <token>tpm_portal</token>.

trans-unit.source: This response code denotes that all the transaction sets in the message/interchange were processed as well as routed successfully.
trans-unit.target: This response code denotes that all the transaction sets in the message/interchange were processed as well as routed successfully.

trans-unit.source: This response code denotes that even though all the transaction sets in the messages/interchange were processed successfully, there were errors while routing one or more of them to the success endpoint.
trans-unit.target: This response code denotes that even though all the transaction sets in the messages/interchange were processed successfully, there were errors while routing one or more of them to the success endpoint.

trans-unit.source: However the ones which could be routed to the success endpoint were routed to the suspend endpoint successfully.
trans-unit.target: However the ones which could be routed to the success endpoint were routed to the suspend endpoint successfully.

trans-unit.source: This response code denotes that one or more transaction sets failed processing.
trans-unit.target: This response code denotes that one or more transaction sets failed processing.

trans-unit.source: The successfully-processed transaction sets are routed to the success endpoint and the others that failed processing are sent to the suspend endpoint.
trans-unit.target: The successfully-processed transaction sets are routed to the success endpoint and the others that failed processing are sent to the suspend endpoint.

trans-unit.source: This response code denotes all other issues that might be encountered while processing transactions set(s) in a message/interchange.
trans-unit.target: This response code denotes all other issues that might be encountered while processing transactions set(s) in a message/interchange.

trans-unit.source: Such a response code is mostly encountered when even the message suspension fails.
trans-unit.target: Such a response code is mostly encountered when even the message suspension fails.
